Hey, you're not out of breath.

00:03:04.660 --> 00:03:06.600
I think I've really gained a lot of stamina!

00:03:06.600 --> 00:03:10.560
They say uphill training has triple 
the effect of level ground.

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:12.350
Seems like we got the desired effect.

00:03:12.350 --> 00:03:15.810
Yeah! I can run 3,200 meters
 without running out of gas!

00:03:15.810 --> 00:03:16.660
Where are you going?

00:03:16.660 --> 00:03:20.400
Gonna run it one more time! 
Actually, two! Well, maybe three!

00:03:20.830 --> 00:03:22.460
Is she serious?

