00:04:10.730 --> 00:04:11.970
It feels wonderful!

00:04:13.040 --> 00:04:14.970
Trainer, she's crazy fast!

00:04:14.970 --> 00:04:17.130
She really seems a lot more powerful.

00:04:17.500 --> 00:04:19.500
Her hindquarters have been strengthened.

00:04:19.780 --> 00:04:23.090
Teio and McQueen have both 
significantly powered up.

00:04:23.510 --> 00:04:26.560
