00:05:38.890 --> 00:05:41.270
There's no hope?

00:05:41.270 --> 00:05:43.560
Staying on the run won't be sufficient.

00:05:43.560 --> 00:05:44.550
Oh, that's what you meant?

00:05:44.550 --> 00:05:47.300
You must <i>significantly</i> outrun them.
 <i>Super</i> outrun them!

00:05:47.300 --> 00:05:49.070
Ultim-outrun them for good fortune!

00:05:49.070 --> 00:05:50.580
Ultimate outrunning?

00:05:50.580 --> 00:05:52.780
Oh, that sounds super for serious!

00:05:52.780 --> 00:05:56.100
All you gotta do now is start running in 
hype mode as soon as the gate pops off!

00:05:57.570 --> 00:05:58.240
Yeah.

00:05:58.710 --> 00:06:01.560
I guess I'll try ultim-outrunning!

00:06:01.560 --> 00:06:04.570
Okay, time for more training!

00:06:04.570 --> 00:06:08.500
I've been losing a lot lately, 
after all. I wanna win.

00:06:08.500 --> 00:06:10.430
I hope I can win next time.

00:06:11.250 --> 00:06:12.710
Tokai Teio!

00:06:13.330 --> 00:06:14.200
Hey.

00:06:14.200 --> 00:06:19.330
I saw you at the Osaka Hai. 
You're must be pretty good to beat our Dictus!

00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:23.140
Next, I'm gonna be taking you on,
 so you better get ready.

00:06:23.140 --> 00:06:24.380
O-Okay...

00:06:24.380 --> 00:06:27.970
I was worried you might've been done 
for when you got injured, though, Teio!

00:06:27.970 --> 00:06:29.420
You did a good job making it back.

00:06:29.420 --> 00:06:31.590
It's important to never give up.

00:06:32.270 --> 00:06:34.010
So I have to work hard.

00:06:35.570 --> 00:06:36.510
You're right!

00:06:36.510 --> 00:06:38.520
I'm gonna work hard on my next race, too!

00:06:38.520 --> 00:06:41.000
Yeah! See you later, Double Turbo!

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:44.900
It's <i>Twin</i> Turbo! I sit, 
like, right next to you!

