00:09:45.370 --> 00:09:47.020
You can do it!

00:09:47.020 --> 00:09:48.500
Palmer!

00:09:49.810 --> 00:09:51.980
You better be vibing out there!

00:09:53.240 --> 00:09:56.590
The ultimate kind of outrunning, 
so no one can catch up to me!

00:09:56.970 --> 00:09:59.790
McQueen is better suited to 
the distance they're running.

00:09:59.790 --> 00:10:03.020
But I just can't picture Teio losing,
 the way she is now.

00:10:03.020 --> 00:10:05.310
It's certainly going to be an amazing race.

00:10:05.310 --> 00:10:07.710
And no matter who wins, 
someone's got to lose.

00:10:07.710 --> 00:10:10.060
Man, racing can be cruel.

00:10:10.060 --> 00:10:14.080
Cruel? I bet you they don't 
